    "### <span style=\"color:  #2980b9  \"> **Working with the OpenFDA API to answer clinical questions**\n",
    "\n",
    "**For each of the below:**\n",
    "1. **Determine if it is possible to answer based on the OpenFDA data.**\n",
    "2. **If it is possible, analyze the data to answer the question.**\n",
    "3. **Add any conclusions you can make based on the data, as possible. Think of this like what you would report back to an executive.**\n",
    "\n",
    "_Note: Your technical approach to answering a question may not exactly match the approach in the answer key as there are many ways to approach these clinical questions. Data science is difficult and there is not always a clear-cut answer. Instead, use the answer key to assess whether your approach is valid._\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
