   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<span style=\"color: #229954 \">**Problem 1: Are there particular patient demographics (e.g., age, sex, weight) or combinations that report higher rates of adverse events with `AMITRIPTYLINE HYDROCHLORIDE`? Limit the data to those reports for adult patients (age >=18) received in 2024.**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "1. Can this be answered? Explain.\n",
    "\n",
    "Yes, the question can be addressed using OpenFDA adverse event data; however, only reporting patterns can be analyzed."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "2. If it can, complete the analysis. If it can't, skip the below cells."
