    "    3. List your findings\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "A total of 500 adverse event reports for Amitriptyline Hydrochloride in 2024 were retrieved using the OpenFDA API due to API result limits.\n",
    "The dataset contains missing values in key demographic fields such as age, sex, and weight, which reduced the number of usable records for analysis.\n",
    "Among records with available information, adverse event reports were more frequently observed in older adults, particularly the 60–74 age group.\n",
    "Female patients appeared more frequently in the available adverse event reports compared to male patients.\n",
    "Weight data was incomplete, but available values were mostly concentrated in the mid-range adult population.\n",
    "The most commonly reported adverse reactions included neurological, gastrointestinal, and psychiatric events."
   ]
